content: <?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>  <reference anchor='I-D.zu-nvo3-user-plane-signalling'> <front> <title>Tenant Traffic Handling in NVO3</title>  <author initials='Z' surname='Qiang' fullname='Zu Qiang'>     <organization /> </author>  <date month='January' day='30' year='2015' />  <abstract><t>This draft discusses the considerations on how to handle the tenant traffic in NVO3 architecture and several related issues which need to be considered when designing a NVO3 based virtualized data center network for multiple tenants.</t></abstract>  </front>  <seriesInfo name='Internet-Draft' value='draft-zu-nvo3-user-plane-signalling-02' /> <format type='TXT'         target='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zu-nvo3-user-plane-signalling-02.txt' /> </reference>
